title: Sample Book (USA), 1899–1901
description: Large book of samples of silk ribbons. Bound in gray cloth. Stickers marked with a "D" are domestic manufacture.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (USA), 1899–1901; paper, silk; H x W: 29.5 x 40.6 cm (11 5/8 x 16 in.); Gift of Herman A. Elsberg; 1936-31-5
